{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act32side", "eventName": "水晶箭行動", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "CR-8", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "一躍而下", "storyInfo": "陽台即將被爆炸吞沒。ELA等人成功逃脫，本想留在陽台的雷內爾則在最後時刻選擇了自救。危機解除後，藝術家們也在克里斯達爾開始了屬於他們自己的狂歡。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "48_g10_deluxeroom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 2.0, "xstrength": 10.0, "ystrength": 10.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_explo_n", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.1}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_explo_n", "volume": 0.5}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.1}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_explo_n", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.1}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_explo_n", "volume": 0.8}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$mutate_intro", "key": "$mutate_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈、哈哈哈哈！", "name": "馬特奧"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們幹得漂亮，然後呢？又能怎麼樣？只能一個不剩地死在這裡！", "name": "馬特奧"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ELA無視像垂死的野獸一樣躺在地上嗥叫個不停的馬特奧，快步走到陽台邊緣。"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_walkfast", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們得稍微做一些超出掛繩使用守則的事了。我需要一個人和我各帶一個人質速降，破窗進入較低樓層。", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_457_blitz_1#4"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "糟了，我們從羅德島出發的時候可沒帶這個。", "name": "BLITZ"}, "figure_art": "char_457_blitz_1#4"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真的？！", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#6$1"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_457_blitz_1#5"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別急，開個玩笑，只是有更好的方法。", "name": "BLITZ"}, "figure_art": "char_457_blitz_1#5"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "更好的？", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#5$1"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_457_blitz_1#6"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "穿上這個。這是我們拜託羅德島的可露希爾小姐製作的多功能噴射滑翔背包。", "name": "BLITZ"}, "figure_art": "char_457_blitz_1#6"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看起來像飛機上的救生衣。", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_457_blitz_1#6"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "外形上就是按照那東西做的，至於用途上嘛，感謝可露希爾小姐，既可以展開滑翔翼滑翔，也可以只用噴射功能協助降落。", "name": "BLITZ"}, "figure_art": "char_457_blitz_1#6"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你確定這東西可靠？", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#10$1"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_457_blitz_1#6"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不然我們是怎麼從六樓進入這棟建築的？", "name": "BLITZ"}, "figure_art": "char_457_blitz_1#6"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 2.0, "xstrength": 10.0, "ystrength": 10.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 50.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_collapse", "volume": 0.4, "loop": "true", "channel": "b"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "b", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_457_blitz_1#6"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "總之，穿上它，拉一下下面的手把，別動上面那個，這東西就會把你安全送到地上。這是你的，ELA。", "name": "BLITZ"}, "figure_art": "char_457_blitz_1#6"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "幫大忙了。", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#8$1"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_armour", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_457_blitz_1#6"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "迪亞茲先生，這是你的。", "name": "BLITZ"}, "figure_art": "char_457_blitz_1#6"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老消防員迅速地把背包套在身上。"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_457_blitz_1#4"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "至於這位雷內爾先生……", "name": "BLITZ"}, "figure_art": "char_457_blitz_1#4"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "BLITZ朝ELA遞了個疑問的眼神，ELA聳了聳肩。"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我答應過別人，如果有機會，會把這傢伙救下來。", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_457_blitz_1#4"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼這個是你的。", "name": "BLITZ"}, "figure_art": "char_457_blitz_1#4"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雷內爾接過背包，卻不穿在身上，只是對著背包出神。"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_457_blitz_1#4"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "先生，我建議你趕緊把它穿好，開玩笑可以，拿自己的生命開玩笑就過頭了。", "name": "BLITZ"}, "figure_art": "char_457_blitz_1#4"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "正好，我記得不久以前你們的ELA小姐說過，她不能保護一個拿自己生命開玩笑的人。", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#8$1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當時我說她誤會了，因為我還有事要做。", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#8$1"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在……我的事總算是塵埃落定，所以……", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#8$1"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "拿命開個玩笑又何妨？", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#9$1"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別傻了，快把它穿好。", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1"}, {"id": 83, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_armour", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雷內爾聳了聳肩，把背包套在自己身上。"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_457_blitz_1#6"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我來打頭陣，請沒用過的各位看清楚了。", "name": "BLITZ"}, "figure_art": "char_457_blitz_1#6"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_explosion", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 4.0, "xstrength": 20.0, "ystrength": 20.0, "vibrato": 90.0, "randomness": 50.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_collapse", "volume": 0.6, "loop": "true", "channel": "b"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "b", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雷內爾向後退了兩步，看著BLITZ翻過陽台邊緣，在空中飄飄搖搖地向下方落去。"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然後是迪亞茲。那個口音和FUZE有幾分類似，但身形更高大一些的男人拍了拍迪亞茲的肩膀，幫他拉下了手柄。"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "陽台上的人們一個接一個地離開，直到站在陽台上的只剩雷內爾和ELA。"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雷內爾還有些遲疑，ELA啟動了兩人的噴射背包，拉著雷內爾向陽台外縱身一躍。"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_steamburst", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovementsp", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_explosion_stone"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_collapse", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 4.0, "xstrength": 40.0, "ystrength": 40.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等等，雷內爾，你做什麼？！", "name": "ELA"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我都說了，用命開個玩笑又何妨？", "name": "雷內爾"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雷內爾脫下了身上的背包，直直地向下落去。"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "耳邊傳來ELA的怒吼，他的腿似乎有一瞬間被ELA抓在手裡，但重力很快將他扯向地面。"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snowstormflp", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "s"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雷內爾不知道自己會落到哪裡，地面還是游泳池，但反正這次他身上沒有安全繩，也沒有背包。"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他試圖品味此刻的失重感與高空彈跳究竟有何區別，他是否在戰慄，而那些戰慄又是否與自己製造的這場盛大的毀滅相襯——"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在他得出結論之前，他忽然覺得手裡鑽進了一枚圓圓的東西，背上被未知的東西弄得有點痛。"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.4, "channel": "a", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "頂著強風強行睜開雙眼，雷內爾隱約看到源石技藝的閃光，同時感受到一些小而硬的圓球抵在自己身下，竭力對抗重力。"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……高爾夫球？", "name": "雷內爾"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不知是突然迸發了求生欲，或者只是被高爾夫球弄得難受，總之，雷內爾選擇了接受。"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他手中的高爾夫球迸發出類似的光芒，引得附近更多的高爾夫球像磁鐵一樣吸到他的背上，一同延緩他下墜的速度——"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "s", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_jump_water", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_underwtr", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "c"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "48_g12_privatebeach", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "c", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_sea", "volume": 0.3, "loop": "true", "channel": "a"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "落入游泳池的雷內爾短暫地浮沉了幾次，最終還是浮在了水面上——"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "更準確地說，是一張由密密麻麻的高爾夫球組成的漂浮墊浮在了水面上，而雷內爾躺在上面。"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他在那張高爾夫球漂浮墊上穩穩當當地站了起來，甚至只跨一步就上了岸。"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#4$1", "posfrom": "-100,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 1.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "米沃什，米沃什！你在哪裡？我知道你在附近！", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#4$1"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "run"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "run", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#10$1", "posfrom": "-200,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 1.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ELA，米沃什呢？", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#7$1"}, {"id": 154, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#10$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不知道，他沒說——", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#10$1"}, {"id": 156, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "200,0", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "站住，你要去哪？", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#6$1"}, {"id": 161, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我去找米沃什。我得把整件事問清楚。", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#6$1"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你覺得自己走得掉嗎？", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#6$1"}, {"id": 166, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你要做什麼，逮捕我？", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#6$1"}, {"id": 168, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在場沒人有那個權限，但你至少應該給被捲入這起事件的人們一個交代。", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#6$1"}, {"id": 170, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "被捲入的人們？", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#6$1"}, {"id": 172, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我從一開始就沒想把你們中的任何一個“捲入其中”。這只是一場關乎毀滅的藝術，除了那些本來就活該的投資客，沒人會受到任何損害。", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#6$1"}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是被慾望沖昏了頭的馬特奧，是多管閒事的迪亞茲……", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#6$1"}, {"id": 175, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……哦，還有你，是你們所有人把事情一步步推到這裡。", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#6$1"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以你自己呢？你就僅僅是一個光榮的反抗者？藝術家？", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#6$1"}, {"id": 179, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我從來都是。", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#6$1"}, {"id": 181, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "知道嗎，你確實是個反抗者，只不過一點都不光榮，你爛透了。", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#6$1"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你剛剛在陽台上到底在發什麼瘋？放棄獲救的機會，這就是你的反抗？", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#6$1"}, {"id": 184, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你到底把死亡看成什麼？展現你厭世氣質的工具？在死亡邊緣踮著腳蹦蹦跳跳的感覺很酷？", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#6$1"}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "讓之前的我，讓米沃什，讓好歹還關心你死活的人每天提心吊膽，這就是你的反抗？", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#6$1"}, {"id": 187, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你在東拉西扯，就為了讓自己的怒氣有個合適的發洩口——", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#6$1"}, {"id": 189, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊，你肯定不同意，你覺得那只是你無關緊要的小癖好，讓別人的投資打水漂才是你真正的反抗。", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#6$1"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦，你一定是覺得投資商虧錢太可憐了，你有不傷害任何人的夢幻般的好辦法——", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#6$1"}, {"id": 193, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "知道嗎，你的爆炸在別人耳中根本就不可能是藝術的悲鳴，只會是瘋子的胡言亂語。", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#6$1"}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你手裡握著父親留下的遺產，你有一萬種方式去表達，去諷刺，去反抗，你偏偏選擇了最懶惰、最難以傳達到其他人心中的一種。", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#6$1"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那只是他們自己不能理解——", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#6$1"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果沒人能理解，你所謂的藝術和反抗又有什麼用？", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#6$1"}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你痛恨你的父親老斯特凡，可你真的認真考慮過該如何反抗嗎？還是說作出一種反抗的姿態就滿足了？", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#6$1"}, {"id": 201, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呵，事到如今誰還在乎？好像只剩你了？", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#6$1"}, {"id": 203, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……混蛋。", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#6$1"}, {"id": 205, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你早就知道我是個混蛋了，不是嗎？", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#6$1"}, {"id": 207, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊，是啊，你這個……", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#6$1"}, {"id": 209, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "a", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "50,0", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 0.2}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "48_i10", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xScaleFrom": 1.0, "yScaleFrom": 1.0, "xScaleTo": 1.05, "yScaleTo": 1.05, "duration": 40.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_cnstrctnck", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$newhope02_intro", "key": "$newhope02_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "徹頭徹尾的混蛋。", "name": "ELA"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你當然可以什麼都不在乎，但米沃什在乎！他甚至不惜把你母親的事告訴我，就為了讓我幫你一把！", "name": "ELA"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "米沃什他？！", "name": "雷內爾"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他說你母親是一個真正熱愛藝術的人，說你曾經是個和她很像的孩子！", "name": "ELA"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "曾經……？", "name": "雷內爾"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不然呢？你覺得你現在跟她有半點相像嗎？", "name": "ELA"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一個熱愛藝術的人，會為了所謂的反抗毀掉無數大師的作品？", "name": "ELA"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "藝術可以是為了真，為了善，為了美，為了反抗惡，或者就為了藝術本身，怎樣都好，每個人都有自己的判斷。", "name": "ELA"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可你所謂的藝術要以其他人的心血為代價，甚至連他人的生命都捲入其中……那不就是單純的惡嗎？", "name": "ELA"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一場爆炸，一片狼藉，一團混亂，這就是你口口聲聲號稱要獻給所有人的“藝術”？！", "name": "ELA"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "問問你自己，你母親會怎麼想？她會為你感到驕傲嗎？", "name": "ELA"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "雷內爾"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真的，雷內爾……", "name": "ELA"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "長大吧。", "name": "ELA"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.03, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.8, "xstrength": 50.0, "ystrength": 50.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_punch02", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.3, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.1, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_jump_water", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ELA一拳揮出，乾脆地砸在雷內爾臉上。"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雷內爾的身體晃了晃，整個人直挺挺地倒回了游泳池裡。"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "48_i11", "screenadapt": "coverall", "xScale": 1.1, "yScale": 1.1, "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xScaleFrom": 1.1, "yScaleFrom": 1.1, "xScaleTo": 1.0, "yScaleTo": 1.0, "duration": 20.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ELA離開了游泳池邊，但雷內爾仍然覺得有雙眼睛在看著自己。"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一個模糊的人影，站在游泳池的另一邊遠遠望著他，臉上的表情說不清到底是關切還是悲哀。"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "上午的陽光刺眼，他看不真切，卻分明覺得那人的眼睛和他母親有幾分相似。"}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他轉頭看向天空，不再去看那個身影。"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而那個人悄然靜立，隨後帶著悲哀的表情默默離開。"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也許自己永遠都不可能成為讓母親驕傲的孩子，那個人也不會願意永遠陪伴自己身邊。"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "最後，自己終究還是孤身一人。"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "想到這裡，那些先前一直煎熬著他的，關於陽奉陰違的疑心和委屈都顯得無足輕重。"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那個人終究還是離開了，此刻，雷內爾心裡只有一個念頭。"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "48_g12_privatebeach", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$saferoom_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_457_blitz_1#4"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "樓裡的事情解決了？", "name": "BLITZ"}, "figure_art": "char_457_blitz_1#4"}, {"id": 275, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4124_iana_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊。", "name": "IANA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4124_iana_1#1$1"}, {"id": 277, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "多索雷斯的警察姍姍來遲，但在聽說所有危險都已經排除之後就展現出了驚人的高效率。", "name": "IANA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4124_iana_1#1$1"}, {"id": 278, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4124_iana_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "尤其是在說“一切都交給我們”的時候，看起來簡直沒有比他們更可靠的人了。", "name": "IANA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4124_iana_1#7$1"}, {"id": 280, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_457_blitz_1#6"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊哈。", "name": "BLITZ"}, "figure_art": "char_457_blitz_1#6"}, {"id": 282, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "樓梯間裡堵著的障礙怎麼樣，他們也清乾淨了？", "name": "BLITZ"}, "figure_art": "char_457_blitz_1#6"}, {"id": 283, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4126_fuze_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……他們有人會專門做這個的源石技藝。看起來就像作弊一樣。", "name": "FUZE"}, "figure_art": "avg_4126_fuze_1#1$1"}, {"id": 285, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_457_blitz_1#6"}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗐，時間長了你就會習慣的。", "name": "BLITZ"}, "figure_art": "char_457_blitz_1#6"}, {"id": 287, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4126_fuze_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過只是好奇，你們是如何在那個時間精準出現在堵塞點以上的樓層的？", "name": "FUZE"}, "figure_art": "avg_4126_fuze_1#1$1"}, {"id": 289, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_458_rfrost_1#1"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "時間上只是個巧合，至於為什麼出現在那個不高不低的樓層……龍舌蘭在給我們發訊息的同時也聯繫了多索雷斯的市長。", "name": "FROST"}, "figure_art": "char_458_rfrost_1#1"}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們抵達市長辦公室的時候，她正在從多個角度實時觀看現場的情況，既有藝術館內部的，也有外部的。", "name": "FROST"}, "figure_art": "char_458_rfrost_1#1"}, {"id": 292, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4124_iana_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "人質裡有她的眼線？", "name": "IANA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4124_iana_1#4$1"}, {"id": 294, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_459_tachak_1"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "差不多。她告訴我們正門大概走不通，然後很慷慨地同意我們從全多索雷斯最高的建築上起跳。", "name": "TACHANKA"}, "figure_art": "char_459_tachak_1"}, {"id": 296, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "其實我們本想直接落在陽台上，給那個上尉來個驚喜的，可惜起跳的高度還是不夠，只好湊合一下。", "name": "TACHANKA"}, "figure_art": "char_459_tachak_1"}, {"id": 297, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "幾人仰頭看向藝術館頂層的陽台，那裡的火已經滅了，只有上尉的一條軟塌塌的手臂，略顯危險地耷拉在空中。"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4125_rdoc_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看來那傢伙不太走運。", "name": "DOC"}, "figure_art": "avg_4125_rdoc_1#1$1"}, {"id": 301, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "DOC話音未落，那條手臂突然動了動，然後在空中張牙舞爪起來，似乎正在被什麼人往回硬拽。"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4125_rdoc_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "收回前言，既沒掉到樓下，又沒葬身火海，最後還被警察救了一命，那傢伙走運過頭了。", "name": "DOC"}, "figure_art": "avg_4125_rdoc_1#10$1"}, {"id": 305, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_282_catap_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ELA，多索雷斯警察局的人希望你們把雷內爾帶過去，他們還說要發個感謝狀給你們，讓你們上個電視什麼的。", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_282_catap_1#9$1"}, {"id": 307, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "上電視，還是和雷內爾一起？算了吧。", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#7$1"}, {"id": 309, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_282_catap_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "埃內斯托也這麼覺得。", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_282_catap_1#10$1"}, {"id": 311, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他還說你們如果沒有在多索雷斯長住的打算，最好不要和市政府方面過多接觸，萬一坎黛拉女士對你們的興趣太大，後續會很麻煩的。", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_282_catap_1#10$1"}, {"id": 312, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那就麻煩警察局的人自己把雷內爾帶走吧。", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1"}, {"id": 314, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_282_catap_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也行，反正他們看起來也不是很著急。", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_282_catap_1#9$1"}, {"id": 316, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "走吧，我們一起去外面逛逛。這座城市雖然紙醉金迷，但也不乏閃光之處。", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#8$1"}, {"id": 318, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_456_ash_1#1"}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不壞。等你們到羅德島補給的時候，再由我們來做導遊。", "name": "ASH"}, "figure_art": "char_456_ash_1#1"}, {"id": 320, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_457_blitz_1#6"}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說到羅德島……DOC，去羅德島的時候，記得包緊一點，戴個帽子什麼的。", "name": "BLITZ"}, "figure_art": "char_457_blitz_1#6"}, {"id": 322, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_457_blitz_1#5"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我帶你去人事部門聊我們小隊漲薪的事情，我說什麼你都點頭就好。尤其是我叫你名字的時候一定要自然。", "name": "BLITZ"}, "figure_art": "char_457_blitz_1#5"}, {"id": 324, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4125_rdoc_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊？", "name": "DOC"}, "figure_art": "avg_4125_rdoc_1#6$1"}, {"id": 326, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "早一步來到泰拉的幾個人，連同空爆都愣了一下，然後笑了起來。"}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_456_ash_1#1"}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "其實是羅德島上有一位——", "name": "ASH"}, "figure_art": "char_456_ash_1#1"}, {"id": 330, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_457_blitz_1#5"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別啊，寇恩，這麼早揭露謎底就不好玩了。", "name": "BLITZ"}, "figure_art": "char_457_blitz_1#5"}, {"id": 332, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_456_ash_1#1"}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（苦笑）好吧。", "name": "ASH"}, "figure_art": "char_456_ash_1#1"}, {"id": 334, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不管怎麼說，能再次見到你們真的是太好了。", "name": "ASH"}, "figure_art": "char_456_ash_1#1"}, {"id": 335, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊。", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#8$1"}, {"id": 337, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "感覺真的是……好久不見了。", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#8$1"}, {"id": 338, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_wind", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "天空晴朗，和風從人工海上吹來，儘管略嫌濕熱，卻也讓人覺得如釋重負。"}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "身後的克里斯達爾藝術館裡傳來和睦的喧囂聲。"}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "48_g6_galleries_b", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_tinnitus", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_dim_openeye", "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "社區居民"}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我這是……", "name": "社區居民"}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_492_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你終於醒啦。", "name": "窘迫的貴族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_492_1#1$1"}, {"id": 361, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你在我家裡幹嘛——不對，這不是我家，是……", "name": "社區居民"}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "糟了！快，快扶我起來，我們還得疏散人群，樓裡還有炸彈！", "name": "社區居民"}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_492_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "整個營救過程中你一直昏著，現在上尉和雷內爾都被抓住，炸彈拆的拆炸的炸，已經到慶功時間了。", "name": "窘迫的貴族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_492_1#1$1"}, {"id": 366, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊？！", "name": "社區居民"}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_033", "posfrom": "0,-50", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 1.2, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.8}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$ddd_intro", "key": "$ddd_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_crwddiscuss_inside", "volume": 0.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "c"}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "channel": "c", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有些發懵的社區居民支起上半身，環顧四周。"}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "展廳裡儼然已經成了藝術家們的狂歡之地。"}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "最引人矚目的當屬展廳中心，那裡已經完全成了一座巨大的舞池，人們在其中忘我地跳著。"}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而圍繞著那座沒有邊界的舞池，自扯畫布的塗鴉，現拉電線的搖滾，爆米花電影輪播……"}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就連小吃攤，都讓藝術家、人質，甚至來辦案的警察駐足停留。"}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_498_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老兄，這麼美味的深盤厚底魔鬼辣椒披薩，現烤的，你真的不來一起嗎？又不收你錢哦！", "name": "社區畫家"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_498_1#1$1"}, {"id": 384, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "多索雷斯警察"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_498_1#1$1"}, {"id": 386, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_498_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別一臉不情願，這東西好吃得你哭出來——喂，我這麼勸你你還臭著一張臉，難道因為你是敘拉古人？", "name": "社區畫家"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_498_1#1$1"}, {"id": 388, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼敘拉古不敘拉古的，因為我認出來了，你這小子在我的警車上噴過塗鴉！", "name": "多索雷斯警察"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_498_1#1$1"}, {"id": 390, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_498_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好像……確實……", "name": "社區畫家"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_498_1#1$1"}, {"id": 392, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哎呀~管那麼多幹嘛咧，總之先嚐嚐披薩嘛！", "name": "社區畫家"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_498_1#1$1"}, {"id": 393, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哼，要不是你們疏散人質做得還不錯，我現在就把你拉到警察局裡。", "name": "多索雷斯警察"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_498_1#1$1"}, {"id": 395, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "警察咬了一口披薩，居然真的有一行清淚流過臉頰。"}}, {"id": 396, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你就用辣椒讓人好吃到哭出來嗎？！", "name": "多索雷斯警察"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_498_1#1$1"}, {"id": 397, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_223"}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "疲憊的羽獸，你要飛向何方♪", "name": "投資界新人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_223"}, {"id": 399, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "才能觸摸到明天的風向♪", "name": "投資界新人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_223"}, {"id": 400, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_001"}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "本以為你這傢伙是個只認識錢的混蛋，喝了點酒居然還會唱搖滾了？", "name": "社區小販"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_001"}, {"id": 402, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_223"}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "開玩笑……我以前是學校搖滾樂隊的主唱！要不是家裡逼得太狠……你以為我願意跟那個老東西點頭哈腰啊！", "name": "投資界新人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_223"}, {"id": 404, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_176"}}, {"id": 405, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "投資界前輩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_176"}, {"id": 406, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_223"}}, {"id": 407, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老東西不在吧？我告訴你們，他最喜歡幹的就是突擊檢查，看你正在用終端幹什麼，沒在工作就扣你薪水！", "name": "投資界新人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_223"}, {"id": 408, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "上次我故意在他來的時候把終端螢幕關上，老東西非要我把螢幕打開，一看全是工作，氣得他直踢我椅子！哈哈！", "name": "投資界新人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_223"}, {"id": 409, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_176"}}, {"id": 410, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你說什麼？！", "name": "投資界前輩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_176"}, {"id": 411, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_223"}}, {"id": 412, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我說什麼？我說的不是事實嗎？", "name": "投資界新人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_223"}, {"id": 413, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老東西，接好了！", "name": "投資界新人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_223"}, {"id": 414, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 415, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 416, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_decap", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 417, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 418, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_cheer_street", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 419, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喝醉了的男人用耳朵開了一瓶啤酒——這個行為為他贏得了滿場歡呼——然後把啤酒潑向台下暴跳如雷的老頭。"}}, {"id": 420, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_202"}}, {"id": 421, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們這下賺大了！不光看了雷內爾的發布會，還逛了藝術館，甚至還現場參加了街頭藝術社區的狂歡節！", "name": "興奮的遊客"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_202"}, {"id": 422, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（小聲）我知道這麼說很過分，但如果沒有馬特奧，我們可能還真沒這運氣——", "name": "興奮的遊客"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_202"}, {"id": 423, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1214_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 424, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "朋友，你認真的？", "name": "迪亞茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1214_1#1$1"}, {"id": 425, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_202"}}, {"id": 426, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不不不，我就是說說，就是說說！", "name": "興奮的遊客"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_202"}, {"id": 427, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1214_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 428, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "都是成年人了，講話注意點。", "name": "迪亞茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1214_1#1$1"}, {"id": 429, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_202"}}, {"id": 430, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "知、知道了，我們去跳舞了！", "name": "興奮的遊客"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_202"}, {"id": 431, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 432, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 433, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 434, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1212_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 435, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老爹，你怎麼一直坐在這裡，不去跟大家一起慶祝？", "name": "特克諾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1212_1#1$1"}, {"id": 436, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1214_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 437, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老爹年紀大了，已經驚心動魄了一上午，就不跟著年輕人一起熱鬧了。", "name": "迪亞茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1214_1#9$1"}, {"id": 438, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1212_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 439, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那我可不陪你了？", "name": "特克諾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1212_1#9$1"}, {"id": 440, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1214_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 441, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "去吧，去跟他們一起熱鬧。", "name": "迪亞茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1214_1#9$1"}, {"id": 442, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 443, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 444, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "特克諾聳了聳肩，往舞池方向走去，嬌小的身影很快消失在人群之中。"}}, {"id": 445, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老消防員也斜著醉眼，不由自主地跟著音樂的節拍抖著腿，看著舞池裡跳個不休的人群。"}}, {"id": 446, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "直到一個人從展場另一端緩緩走來，散發著與眼前的歡鬧和喧囂格格不入的氣場。"}}, {"id": 447, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 448, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 449, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1214_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 450, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 451, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 452, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#1$1", "posfrom": "300,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 453, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 454, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦，迪亞茲，恭喜你，你們最後還是在我家裡把派對開了起來。", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#1$1"}, {"id": 455, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1214_1#10$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 456, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有意見？", "name": "迪亞茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1214_1#10$1"}, {"id": 457, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 458, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我可沒那麼小心眼，不會因為一個蠢貨的挑撥就熱血上頭，上個大當。", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#1$1"}, {"id": 459, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1214_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 460, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那也不壞。去舞池裡跳上一曲如何？", "name": "迪亞茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1214_1#9$1"}, {"id": 461, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 462, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……不用了。", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#2$1"}, {"id": 463, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1214_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 464, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦，你的“舞伴”不在這裡，他好像不想再跟你跳下來了。", "name": "迪亞茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1214_1#9$1"}, {"id": 465, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 466, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "胡扯。", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#7$1"}, {"id": 467, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你呢，你不也一個人坐在這裡喝啤酒？你的舞伴又在哪裡？", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#7$1"}, {"id": 468, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1214_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 469, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這你可問錯人了。", "name": "迪亞茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1214_1#9$1"}, {"id": 470, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果我想跳，除了你，此時此刻，展廳裡的每個人都能成為我的舞伴。", "name": "迪亞茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1214_1#9$1"}, {"id": 471, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 472, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 473, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 474, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 475, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 476, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 477, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 478, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}